paul_f(-at-)ntlworld.com writes:
how were these done without seriously reducing the strength of the bus - ie 
removing the bulkhead?
Hi Paul,
By building them on walk thru front sheetmetal that allows the walk through 
buses to not have body flex problems that a normal non-walk through bus would 
have if the bulkhead was cut out!
Eric&Barb
